UPS Status

Status
Indicates the general status of the UPS: OK, on battery, bypass, and more.
Input Voltage
Current level of voltage input.
Input Frequency
Current frequency of input.
Output Voltage
Current level of UPS output voltage.
Output Frequency
Current frequency of output.
Load
Current load in percent in terms of battery power.
Seconds on Battery
System counter in seconds during the "on battery" status.
Battery Voltage
Current UPS battery voltage.
Battery Capacity
Charge level of UPS battery in percent.
Autonomy Time
Calculated estimate of time remaining under the current load after which battery capacity will be exhausted.
Battery Temperature
Current temperature of UPS battery.
This is both a graphical and numerical display of the current UPS load in percent of total available capacity.
This is both a graphical and numerical display of the current UPS battery level in percent of total charging capacity.
